{"tid":2380500,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"至今共有4名港人獲德國政治庇護","createTime":"2021-01-26T02:38:14.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-26T15:20:32.000Z","uid":240362,"like":18,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"15de55629600bffc8b01dc02511ba51e643d467d","tid":2380500,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-26T02:38:14.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1572360-20210126.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1572360-20210126.htm&d=KsvwSKeUMZz4C4B35sIM%2BCq0XD4M5CHb8byFtBYuAsM%3D&h=1a679e44\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1572360-20210126.htm&h=8e306a19\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1572360-20210126.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n德國國會就香港國安法舉行聽證會，德國外交部亞太司長席格孟特透露歐盟正考慮實施制裁。<br />\n<br />\n聽證會由在漢堡留學的港人鄺頌晴和德國記者穆達偉去年7月提出。<br />\n<br />\n席格孟特表示，香港警隊根據國安法鎮壓和平示威，破壞歐盟對中國履行國際義務的信任，德國已中止與香港的引渡協議，並停止向香港出口可能鎮壓人權的物資。<br />\n<br />\n她說，歐盟去年建立對全球侵犯人權者的制裁機制，透露歐盟正密切觀察和討論香港局勢，考慮採用這套機制，目標是盡快結束討論，但要全體會員國同意需要時間。<br />\n<br />\n鄺頌晴發言時促請德國設立「逃生艇」計劃，讓港人無需簽證入境等。她又要求歐洲議會通過決議制裁中港官員，叫停「中歐投資協議」。<br />\n<br />\n席格孟特表示，基本上港人無需簽證可到歐盟，德國已放寬港人居留規定，又提供獎學金給香港學者，歡迎他們來德國居住和工作。她還透露，目前有4名港人獲德國政治庇護。"},{"pid":"36a2f1a77fd8c6cc814a5ea88053b83bcf8310bd","tid":2380500,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-26T02:42:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2b2a1fbb0c10930fb29f3bf5d6532825cf79aa1","tid":2380500,"uid":229275,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-01-26T03:17:51.000Z","msg":"黃台仰， 李東昇，先前有一個喺難民營被性侵嘅手足，再加多一個"},{"pid":"31ee9b1e3689a0d26708f24b586661661e2df08c","tid":2380500,"uid":51752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-26T04:12:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0cc952348a905691fac8de49a9eba8bc65ab5d3c","tid":2380500,"uid":283970,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"c2b2a1fbb0c10930fb29f3bf5d6532825cf79aa1","tid":2380500,"uid":229275,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-01-26T03:17:51.000Z","msg":"黃台仰， 李東昇，先前有一個喺難民營被性侵嘅手足，再加多一個"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-26T04:22:46.000Z","msg":"其實唔多唔少個主因係德國屬於非英語系國家，即使獲得難民簽證，往後嘅生活會比五眼等地區難度高啲，雖則德國人普遍英語能力高，但要融入當地始終不能單靠英文。<br />\n<br />\n即使係咁，如果有人真係覺得有人身安全問題，唔應該考慮語言，正如你響沙漠缺水情況下，尿你都要飲，唔係就生存唔到。"},{"pid":"06d569cb6334203c369617c45bb2175020e25b6c","tid":2380500,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-26T05:43:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b84ada4f36ba25cacad6ad7d36fbe31cd7130c0","tid":2380500,"uid":212274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-26T05:54:33.000Z","msg":"個議會成個遊戲場景咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ac6df80ba435a673a5cff240db74b5a14ba88fe","tid":2380500,"uid":232157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-26T13:01:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8de5387b1728899c99186e22a6e53e4693874f13","tid":2380500,"uid":14867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c2b2a1fbb0c10930fb29f3bf5d6532825cf79aa1","tid":2380500,"uid":229275,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-01-26T03:17:51.000Z","msg":"黃台仰， 李東昇，先前有一個喺難民營被性侵嘅手足，再加多一個"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-